{
  "stem": "16345.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where there, there were some good things happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Allies, the Americans and English in particular, were bombing Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we liked it, even though some of us were killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in, in Braunschweig, we were working in a place called the diesel bunker.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were producing engines for trucks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is diesel-- D-I-E-S-E--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "D-I-E-S-E-L.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called a bunker-- B-U-N-K-E-R.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it was an, an underground factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we worked the night shift, 12 hours night shift.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every time there was an air raid, they would turn off the lights.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were made to sit-in a corner, which was a lot of fun.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we were resting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was very hard work, particularly-- my father was working as a mechanic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was a mechanic's helper, which means I had to move those heavy motors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I became quite adept at it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, they, they weigh several pounds, very heavy cast iron motors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I sort of teeter tottered them from one station to another.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when another guy who was doing the same kind of work-- the motor dropped.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he lost several toes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was never seen again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Also, they told us if we-- if one of those motors dropped, they were cast iron.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And if they, if they dropped, some of them busted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They fractured.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was also a death sentence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we had, we had reason to be good workers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Also, we were working with French prisoners of war in that place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were not allowed to talk to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But there was one prisoner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were getting rations of beer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You know, in Germany, they used to drink beer like in this country drink coffee or orange juice.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
